# Meross MQTT Bridge
# ------------------
# This project uses config/config.yaml for all configuration.
# No .env file is needed.
#
# To get started:
#   1. docker compose up -d
#   2. Open the GUI at http://localhost:8080
#   3. Log in with admin / admin (you'll be prompted to change your password)
#   4. Configure your Meross credentials and MQTT broker in Settings
#   5. Configure your doors in Doors
#
# The bridge will automatically connect once credentials are configured.
